  "detailed_description": "In Outbreak Overlord, you are the mastermind behind the zombie apocalypse. Starting with just one infected, you must strategically bite civilians and soldiers to expand your horde.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850890/extras/42dcaee3b9e373d709e75f66c67f8dc6.poster.avif?t=1730140091\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850890/extras/42dcaee3b9e373d709e75f66c67f8dc6.webm?t=1730140091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850890/extras/42dcaee3b9e373d709e75f66c67f8dc6.mp4?t=1730140091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Craft tactics to infect heavily armed soldiers and develop your strategy to turn every inhabitant into a loyal undead follower. Unleash a decisive attack, showcasing all your ingenuity.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850890/extras/f6620b72bee0e912577a4d6fac9de40a.poster.avif?t=1730140091\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850890/extras/f6620b72bee0e912577a4d6fac9de40a.webm?t=1730140091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850890/extras/f6620b72bee0e912577a4d6fac9de40a.mp4?t=1730140091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The world is divided into various survivor communities. Each community is working on a cure for the infection in research centers. Think of the best way to spread chaos until there is no possibility of a cure left on the planet.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850890/extras/824cc02f9a239ab52dfb026b8ea48935.poster.avif?t=1730140091\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850890/extras/824cc02f9a239ab52dfb026b8ea48935.webm?t=1730140091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850890/extras/824cc02f9a239ab52dfb026b8ea48935.mp4?t=1730140091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
